translated: Brilioth, Brita, Bishop, Växjö, born 12/12/1896 in Paris to Archbishop Nathan Söderblom and Anna Forsell. Married in 1919 to Bishop Yngve Brilioth. Children: see him. - Studied in Paris, Büttnersche höhere Mädchenschule in Leipzig from 1912-1914 and in Uppsala, Swedish schools and private gymnasiums. Visited England and Finland. Vice-chairman of Kronoberg County Disaster Relief Committee, Board member of deaf and dumb school, member of Växjö Diocesan Women's Council. Fluent in Swedish, Danish and English.
